react-chartjs:

installation:
- chart.js
- react-chartjs-2


step 1: register important elements from the chartjs
		--> ChartJS.register()
		
step 2: use react-charts-2 components like Bar, Line, Pie etc. with data as an attribute

data structure:

data = {
	labels: x-axis-values[],
	datasets:[{
		label: ,
		data: y-axis-values[],
		backgroundColor:[], // this will be as much as the number of items in dataset's data i.e can set color for each y-values
		borderColor: string,
		borderWidth: number,
	}]
}
